{"id":295849,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/global-voices-网络过滤机制将随著作权法修正案进入台湾/","date":"2013-05-29T11:45:50Z","modified":"2013-05-29T11:45:50Z","title":"Global Voices | 网络过滤机制将随著作权法修正案进入台湾","content":"<p><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.tipo.gov.tw/\">台湾经济部智慧财产局（IPO）</a>中最近<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com.tw/n60576/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E6%90%B6%E5%85%88%E7%9C%8B-%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E5%B1%80%E6%93%AC%E6%93%8B%E5%A2%83%E5%A4%96%E4%BE%B5%E6%AC%8A%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99.html\">拟</a>中修正《著作权法》，以提供法律依据，合法透过黑名单的方式，于<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISP\">网路服务提供者</a>（ISP）层级，封锁<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_Protocol\">IP</a>位址与<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Domain_Name_System\">DNS</a>。智财局宣称，该修正案能制止非法分享受著作权法保护的电影与音乐。</p>\n<p>尽管智财局强调，ISP业者未来只会封锁境外“专门从事著作权侵权行为”的网路平台，或是“明显违反著作权”的网站，譬如网站Megaupload。政府当局未来将会锁定点对点传输（peer-to-peer transmission）的网路平台，<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BitTorrent_(protocol)\">BT(Bit Torrent)</a>、<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Foxy_(P2P)\">Foxy</a>与<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/FTP\">FTP</a>等分享皆包含在内。</p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/oiwan/\" title=\"文章导读 Oiwan Lam\">Oiwan Lam</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/ameli/\" title=\"文章导读 Ameli\">Ameli</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/05/26/netizens-fear-copyright-amendment-will-bring-web-filter-system-to-taiwan/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/05/29/12558/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%B0%86%E9%9A%8F%E8%91%97%E4%BD%9C%E6%9D%83%E6%B3%95%E4%BF%AE%E6%AD%A3%E6%A1%88%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F05%2F29%2F12558%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F05%2F29%2F12558%2F&#038;desc=%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%B0%86%E9%9A%8F%E8%91%97%E4%BD%9C%E6%9D%83%E6%B3%95%E4%BF%AE%E6%AD%A3%E6%A1%88%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:var js=document.createElement (\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F05%2F29%2F12558%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F05%2F29%2F12558%2F&#038;text=%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%B0%86%E9%9A%8F%E8%91%97%E4%BD%9C%E6%9D%83%E6%B3%95%E4%BF%AE%E6%AD%A3%E6%A1%88%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F05%2F29%2F12558%2F&#038;title=%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%B0%86%E9%9A%8F%E8%91%97%E4%BD%9C%E6%9D%83%E6%B3%95%E4%BF%AE%E6%AD%A3%E6%A1%88%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B0%E6%